snippet.title: WH40K: Regicide Let's Play - Snakebites Vs Ultramarines
snippet.description:
Hammerfall_Ally and Junglist play as the Ultramarines and Snakebites with their brand new unique faction abilities. 
This update and more coming late May with the Regicide iOS launch.
To read more about unique faction abilities, check out the Regicide Dev Blog: http://www.warhammer40kregicide.com/news/blog/april-2016/unique-faction-abilities-feature-showcase

Buy Regicide on Steam now:
http://steamcommunity.com/app/322910/
